name: Experiment Or Die #78
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. Todays design is an homage to Mumbot and her character Mossy as her birthday is tomorrow. The texture I was able to get on this piece is unreal. I'm not even sure where some of it came from. Static and scratch emerging from the layers. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk.
